{"word":"δίω","slug":"δίω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n27742\" key=\"di/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">δίω</orth> <pron extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pron\">[ῐ]</pron>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> Verb (used also by <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> </bibl> in lyr. passages, <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.</abbr> sub fin.), only <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ pres.\">pres.</a></tns> and <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ impf.\">impf.</a></tns> <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></gram> </gramGrp> (of which <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> has <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ subj.\">subj.</a></mood> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δίωμαι, δίηται, δίωνται,</foreign> opt. <sense id=\"n27742.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">δίοιτο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:17:317\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.317</biblScope></bibl></cit>, but mostly <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δίεσθαι;</foreign> for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δίον</foreign> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">v.</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform